props.name: rowMapping
props.value:
(item, index) => [
							<Box key={`${index}_source`}>
								<SolaceTooltip variant={TooltipVariant.overflow} title={item.source}>
									<SolaceTypography noWrap={true}>{item.source}</SolaceTypography>
								</SolaceTooltip>
							</Box>,
							<Box key={`${index}_target`}>
								<SolaceTooltip variant={TooltipVariant.overflow} title={item.target}>
									<SolaceTypography noWrap={true}>{item.target}</SolaceTypography>
								</SolaceTooltip>
							</Box>
						]
